{"tid":1879616,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節短故《疫情人節》","createTime":"2020-02-14T09:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T15:18:37.000Z","uid":84696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c301d90e46f1734de182543e427a63bc897c940","tid":1879616,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"情人節短故《疫情人節》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我現在身處於黃金太子號，今天是二月十四日情人節。因<br />\n<br />\n為早前的疫情影響，一眾乘客被隔離在船上已經是第十四<br />\n<br />\n日，聽說還有五天，我們就可以下船了，但根本是在等<br />\n<br />\n死，你們絕對想不到這裡的環境非常惡劣，不......是煉獄一<br />\n<br />\n樣!<br />\n<br />\n政府及電視台對外發佈的消息是虛假的，那些狀況安好<br />\n<br />\n的畫面全是模擬。2月1日，船上一名老翁確診患病的那一<br />\n<br />\n天開始，事件變得不可收拾......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「好凍.....」她躺在地上滿身顫動說道。<br />\n<br />\n我的未婚妻患有心律不正，隨身的藥因意外丢失了，沒有<br />\n<br />\n糧食，只靠飲用污水的期間，加上這幾天的搏鬥，她快將<br />\n<br />\n捱不下去。<br />\n<br />\n「冇野架，好快離開哩到。吖，今日情人節，我地不如慶祝......」<br />\n<br />\n我在廚房東翻西找，終於找來了血淋淋的發臭肉，把爐火<br />\n<br />\n開着，準備一場黑暗中的晚餐。<br />\n<br />\n「等等就有得食，而家播首歌聽。」<br />\n<br />\n「Every night in my dreams<br />\n<br />\nI see you, I feel you<br />\n<br />\nThat is how I know you go on<br />\n<br />\nFar across the distance<br />\n<br />\nAnd spaces between us<br />\n<br />\nYou have come to show you go on.」<br />\n<br />\n「boom boom boom!」<br />\n<br />\n外面傳來強烈撞擊聲，我沒有理會，專心把食物煮好，也找來蠟燭點燃，走到她的身旁。<br />\n<br />\n她連說話的氣力都沒有，閉起雙眼，只是在微笑。<br />\n<br />\n「boom!」<br />\n<br />\n門終於被撞開了!<br />\n<br />\n「You're here, there's nothing I fear<br />\n<br />\nAnd I know that my heart will go on<br />\n<br />\nWe'll stay forever this way<br />\n<br />\nYou are safe in my heart and<br />\n<br />\nMy heart will go on and on」<br />\n<br />\n我抱着她蜷縮一角，看着迎面而來的「乘客」，最後一句<br />\n<br />\n話就是:<br />\n<br />\n「情人節快樂!」<br />\n<br />\nEnd😂"},{"pid":"f8948e967c6ec0982aad3cbbef63f8a765d158d8","tid":1879616,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"本身係想寫喪屍長故，不過唔擅長作哩類就點到即止算<br />\n<br />\nANYWAY， 情人節快樂!"},{"pid":"ae779484803638ceaf9ebff411b6b6eb293bab9f","tid":1879616,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85960316061d5c1dbf89d23b07f980375abd9198","tid":1879616,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae779484803638ceaf9ebff411b6b6eb293bab9f","tid":1879616,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"冇啊，見情人節，哩個當玩下咁寫，冇咩信心作長篇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68328e6cee924ad14f5ff70de3cd65f795c3b7af","tid":1879616,"uid":52238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"短故真係好短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997732abc98250b5f3dfd8261e6c7d8abf565cc0","tid":1879616,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68328e6cee924ad14f5ff70de3cd65f795c3b7af","tid":1879616,"uid":52238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"短故真係好短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:23:38.000Z","msg":"寫唔到有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410a1da81ebe5ac65239952e9d7c94c56e889996","tid":1879616,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"巴打啲排版有少少問題"},{"pid":"e945407b1f83bd3f3e5f90875ce92767ec1694fc","tid":1879616,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410a1da81ebe5ac65239952e9d7c94c56e889996","tid":1879616,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:55